Automatic Deployment

1. Create SSH alias corresponding to the IP address of the Raspberry Pi Zero.
    Host devbox
        User Pi
        HostName 192.168.0.0
        IdentityFile ~/.ssh/rsa_id

2. Share the user account public key with Raspberry Pi Zero ssh-copy-id.

3. Start ssh-agent and ssh-add in shell that is used to instantiate the CLion instance.